    <h1>Delete Your Account – Hoarding Support</h1>
    <p>We respect your privacy and your right to control your data. You can delete your account from within the app or request it manually here.</p>

    <h2>🗑️ Delete via the App</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the <strong>Hoarding Support</strong> app</li>
      <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong></li>
      <li>Tap <strong>“Delete My Account”</strong></li>
      <li>Confirm deletion — this will permanently remove your account, photos, goals, XP, and all saved data from our servers.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>🌐 Request Manual Deletion</h2>
    <p>If you no longer have access to the app or prefer to delete your account outside of it, you can use the form below:</p>
    <p><a href="https://forms.gle/YOUR_FORM_LINK_HERE" target="_blank">👉 Request Account Deletion via Form</a></p>

    <h2>🔐 What Happens When You Delete Your Account?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Your profile and associated data (goals, photos, progress, etc.) will be permanently deleted.</li>
      <li>Your data cannot be recovered once deleted.</li>
      <li>Deletion requests are processed within 48 hours.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact us at:<br/>
    <strong>Email:</strong> support@hoardingsupport.app</p>
